{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"prefersPointerLocked"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":". Setting this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" indicates the view’s preference to lock the pointer, although the system may not honor the request."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For the system to consider locking the pointer:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The scene must be full screen, not in Split View or Slide Over, with no other apps in Slide Over."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The scene must be in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIScene.ActivationState.foregroundActive"},{"type":"text","text":" state."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In Mac Catalyst, the app must be in the foreground, and the window that contains the scene ordered to the front."}]}]}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bringing a Mac Catalyst app to the foreground doesn’t immediately enable pointer lock."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To enable pointer lock, the user must click in the window."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To exit pointer lock, users can use cmd-tab to switch to another app, or using cmd-tilde."}]}]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing this property makes an effect only starting from iOS 14."}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The system continuously monitors the state and when the app no longer satisfies the requirements, it disables the pointer lock."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the lock state changes, the system posts "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIPointerLockState.didChangeNotification"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":1,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/sheekit\/uiviewcontrollerproxy\/preferspointerlocked"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SheeKit\/documentation\/SheeKit\/UIViewControllerProxy\/prefersPointerLocked","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Specifies whether the view prefers to lock the pointer to a specific scene."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"prefersPointerLocked"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"title":"prefersPointerLocked","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:7SheeKit21UIViewControllerProxyV20prefersPointerLockedSbSgvp","modules":[{"name":"SheeKit"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SheeKit\/documentation\/SheeKit","doc:\/\/SheeKit\/documentation\/SheeKit\/UIViewControllerProxy"]]},"references":{"doc://SheeKit/documentation/SheeKit/UIViewControllerProxy":{"role":"symbol","title":"UIViewControllerProxy","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"UIViewControllerProxy"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy with preferred parameters of the presented view controller that hosts the presented "},{"type":"codeVoice","